      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Saern — Korre Agent</h2><p>One of V. Korre's two paid agents. Handles forgery, lock work, and packet-burning. <strong>In the cistern climax, Saern's combat priority is the brazier — he will move directly there and start burning the packet within two rounds.</strong></p><p><em>Stat: Tough / Thug analog (CR 1/2).</em></p>",
